gations%20where%20conversions%20are%20taking%20place%20must%20be%20stopped%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20has%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20country's%20%26quot%3Bmajority%20population%20would%20be%20in%20minority%26quot%3B%20if%20such%20gatherings%20are%20allowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20was%20hearing%20yesterday%20the%20bail%20petition%20of%20Kailash%2C%20who%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20taking%20people%20from%20Hamirpur%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20a%20gathering%20in%20Delhi%20for%20conversions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20order%20says%20that%20according%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20Kailash%20took%20Ramkali%20Prajapati's%20brother%20Ramphal%20to%20Delhi%20and%20he%20never%20returned%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamphal%2C%20the%20FIR%20has%20said%2C%20had%20been%20suffering%20from%20mental%20illness%20and%20Kailash%20said%20that%20he%20will%20be%20treated%20at%20the%20gathering%20in%20Delhi%20and%20will%20be%20home%20in%20a%20week.%20When%20Ramphal%20did%20not%20return%2C%20she%20asked%20Kailash%20but%20did%20not%20get%20a%20satisfactory%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20says%20that%20many%20people%20from%20the%20Hamirpur%20village%20were%20taken%20to%20the%20Delhi%20gathering%20and%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%20Kailash%20was%20arrested%20under%20charges%20of%20kidnapping%20and%20provisions%20of%20UP%20Prohibition%20of%20Unlawful%20Conversion%20of%20Religion%20Act%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government's%20counsel%2C%20Additional%20Advocate%20General%20PK%20Giri%2C%20told%20the%20court%20that%20at%20such%20gatherings%2C%20a%20huge%20number%20of%20people%20are%20being%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%20He%20also%20pointed%20to%20statements%20of%20witnesses%20who%20have%20said%20Kailash%20had%20been%20taking%20people%20from%20the%20village%20for%20conversion%20and%20was%20getting%20paid%20in%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKailash's%20counsel%20Saket%20Jaiswal%20said%20Ramphal%20was%20not%20converted%20to%20Christianity%20and%20had%20only%20attended%20a%20Christian%20gathering.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20Sonu%20Paster%20who%20was%20holding%20such%20gathering%2C%20and%20he%20has%20already%20been%20enlarged%20on%20bail%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Rohit%20Ranjan%20Agarwal%20said%20in%20his%20order%20that%20Article%2025%20of%20the%20Constitution%20provides%20for%20freedom%20of%20conscience%20and%20free%20profession%2C%20practice%2C%20and%20propagation%20of%20religion%2C%20but%20does%20not%20provide%20for%20conversion%20from%20one%20faith%20to%20another%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20word%20'Propagation'%20means%20to%20promote%2C%20but%20it%20does%20not%20mean%20to%20convert%20any%20person%20from%20his%20religion%20to%20another%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20Ramphal%20never%20returned%20to%20the%20village%20and%20that%20several%20witnesses%20have%20accused%20Kailash%20of%20taking%20away%20people%20for%20conversion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20process%20is%20allowed%20to%20be%20carried%20out%2C%20the%20majority%20population%20of%20this%20country%20would%20be%20in%20minority%20one%20day%2C%20and%20such%20religious%20congregation%20should%20be%20immediately%20stopped%20where%20the%20conversion%20is%20taking%20place%20and%20changing%20religion%20of%20citizen%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%2C%20while%20denying%20bail%20to%20Kailash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20come%20into%20notice%20of%20this%20Court%20in%20several%20cases%20that%20unlawful%20activity%20of%20conversion%20of%20people%20of%20SC%2FST%20castes%20and%20other%20castes%20including%20economically%20poor%20persons%20into%20Christianity%20is%20being%20done%20at%20rampant%20pace%20throughout%20the%20State%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719893760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmpbrq8a_all