ood%20actor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbreakthrough-in-salman-khan-firing-case-audio-of-gangsters-call-to-shooter-5944615%5C%22%3ESalman%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20revealed%20chilling%20details.%20According%20to%20the%20Navi%20Mumbai%20Police%2C%20the%20accused%2C%20associated%20with%20the%20notorious%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20conspiracy%20to%20murder%20and%20other%20grave%20offences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2014%2C%20Two%20men%20on%20motorbikes%20fired%20multiple%20rounds%20outside%20Mr%20Khan's%20residence%20in%20Bandra%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20several%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20charge%20sheet%2C%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20had%20issued%20a%20contract%20worth%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20to%20assassinate%20the%20actor.%20The%20plan%20was%20hatched%20over%20several%20months%2C%20from%20August%202023%20to%20April%202024.%20Investigations%20have%20revealed%20that%20the%20gang%20intended%20to%20acquire%20advanced%20firearms%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20including%20AK-47s%2C%20AK-92s%2C%20M16%20rifles%2C%20and%20the%20Turkish-made%20Zigana%20pistol%2C%20the%20weapon%20used%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Punjabi%20singer%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala%20on%20May%2029%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conspiracy%20wasn't%20merely%20confined%20to%20acquiring%20weapons%3B%20it%20extended%20to%20a%20well-orchestrated%20surveillance%20operation.%20According%20to%20the%20charge%20sheet%2C%20a%20network%20of%20approximately%2060%20to%2070%20individuals%20was%20involved%20in%20tracking%20Mr%20Khan's%20every%20movement.%20This%20extensive%20surveillance%20covered%20his%20residence%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20his%20Panvel%20farmhouse%2C%20and%20even%20the%20Goregaon%20Film%20City%2C%20where%20he%20often%20visited%20for%20film%20shoots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charge%20sheet%20claims%20that%20boys%20below%20the%20age%20of%2018%20were%20recruited%20to%20execute%20the%20assassination.%20These%20minors%20were%20reportedly%20waiting%20for%20orders%20from%20Goldie%20Brar%20and%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%2C%20key%20figures%20in%20the%20gang%20believed%20to%20be%20operating%20from%20North%20America%2C%20to%20initiate%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20the%20shooting%20incident%20outside%20Mr%20Khan's%20home%2C%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20met%20with%20the%20actor%20and%20assured%20all%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20is%20with%20you%2C%20I%20have%20told%20Salman%20Khan.%20Both%20the%20accused%20have%20been%20arrested.%20They%20will%20be%20interrogated.%20We%20will%20get%20to%20the%20root%20of%20the%20case.%20Nobody%20will%20be%20spared.%20Nobody%20should%20targeted%20this%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Eknath%20Shinde%20told%20reporters%20outside%20the%20actor's%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20gang%20or%20gang%20war%20will%20be%20allowed.%20We%20won't%20allow%20this%20to%20happen.%20We%20will%20finish%20(Lawrence)%20Bishnoi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719892140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fier7doko_salman-khan_625x300_17_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsalman-khan-lawrence-bishnoi-goldie-brar-zigana-guns-rs-25-lakh-contract-bishnoi-gangs-plan-to-kill-salman-khan-6014783%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20Navi%20Mumbai%20Police%2C%20the%20accused%2C%20associated%20with%20the%20notorious%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20conspiracy%20to%20murder%20and%20other%20grave%20offences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsalman-khan-lawrence-bishnoi-goldie-brar-zigana-guns-rs-25-lakh-contract-bishnoi-gangs-plan-to-kill-salman-khan-6014783%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsalman-khan-lawrence-bis