A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Faustralian-firms-given-six-months-to-develop-code-to-prevent-children-from-seeing-porn%2Farticleshow%2F111418386.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Faustralian-firms-given-six-months-to-develop-code-to-prevent-children-from-seeing-porn%2Famp_articleshow%2F111418386.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Faustralian-firms-given-six-months-to-develop-code-to-prevent-children-from-seeing-porn%2Famp_articleshow%2F111418386.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Malaysia's%20%24100%20billion%20ghost%20town%20is%20good%20for%20at%20least%20one%20thing%3A%20filming%20documentaries%20and%20shows%20like%20Netflix's%20'The%20Mole'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224447%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20mall%20without%20people%20in%20malaysia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66012a0a3f923f7dab00a5eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223339%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EForest%20City's%20mall%20was%20empty%20when%20Business%20Insider%20visited%20last%20year.%3Cp%3EMarielle%20Descalsota%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EForest%20City%2C%20Malaysia%20was%20used%20as%20a%20set%20for%20a%20Netflix%20reality%20show%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Mole.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPlanned%20as%20a%20%24100%20billion%20mega-complex%2C%20Forest%20City%20has%20become%20a%20ghost%20town%20with%20few%20residents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDevelopers%20face%20financial%20issues%2C%20because%20less%20than%2015%25%20of%20the%20project%20is%20completed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMalaysia's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforest-city-ghost-town-malaysia-hotel-golf-beach-tourist-singapore-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24100%20billion%20ghost%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20meant%20to%20house%20700%2C000%20people.%20After%20few%20people%20moved%20in%2C%20developers%20tried%20in%20vain%20to%20make%20it%20into%20a%20tourist%20hub.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20mega-development%20is%20serving%20as%20a%20set%20for%20a%20handful%20of%20reality%20shows%20and%20documentaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20empty%20city%2C%20just%20over%20Singapore's%20western%20border%2C%20was%20used%20for%20an%20episode%20on%20the%20second%20season%20of%20Netflix%20reality%20show%20%26quot%3BThe%20Mole%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20debuted%20last%20week.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20competition-style%20reality%20series%20follows%2012%20contestants%20completing%20challenges%20while%20one%20of%20them%20secretly%20sabotages%20the%20other%20players.%20They%20race%20to%20grow%20a%20money%20pot%20prize%20and%20uncover%20who%20the%20traitor%20is%20among%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20show's%2010-episode%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esecond%20season%20was%20filmed%20entirely%20in%20Malaysia%20and%20features%20Forest%20City%2C%20Kuala%20Lumpur%2C%20and%20Tioman%20Island.%20Filming%20started%20in%20July%202023%20and%20lasted%20for%20six%20weeks%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsays.com%2Fmy%2Fentertainment%2Fthe-mole-netflix-filmed-in-malaysia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20media.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20contestants%2C%20who%20come%20from%20various%20professional%20backgrounds%2C%20complete%20treasure%20hunts%2C%20free%20dive%2C%20and%20abseil%20down%20a%2038-story%20building%20in%20Forest%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20third%20episode%20of%20the%20season%2C%20show%20host%20and%20former%20NPR%20journalist%20Ari%20Shapiro%20introduced%20Forest%20City%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20perfect%20spot%20for%20a%20glamorous%20holiday%20home%2C%20for%20those%20who%20can%20afford%20it.%20And%20most%20of%20the%20year%2C%20they%20lie%20empty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20was%20also%20featured%20in%20recent%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea's%20KBS%20filmed%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20travel%20reality%20series%20%26quot%3BBattle%20Trip%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20German%20ProSieben%20TV%20filmed%20a%20short%20documentary%20about%20Forest%20City.%20An%20Austrian%20documentary%20titled%20%26quot%3BHungry%3A%20Tipping%20the%20Scales%26quot%3B%20shot%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnnounced%20in%202006%2C%20the%20luxury%20housing%20project%20was%20meant%20to%20feature%20apartments%2C%20a%20waterpark%2C%20and%20hotels.%20The%20whole%20project%20cost%20its%20developers%20%24100%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20eight%20years%20after%20construction%20began%2C%20only%20a%20few%20thousand%20people%20live%20there.%20The%20project%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforest-city-ghost-town-malaysia-hotel-golf-beach-tourist-singapore-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eghost%20town%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20major%20liability%20for%20its%20developer%2C%20Country%20Garden%2C%20which%20is%20facing%20sizable%20financial%20issues%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.channelnewsasia.com%2Fasia%2Fjohor-country-garden-forest-city-property-crisis-debt-china-3715791%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%20about%2015%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20planned%20property%20had%20been%20completed%2C%20while%20most%20finished%20apartments%20appear%20never%20to%20have%20been%20lived%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20and%20Forest%20City%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmalaysia-100-billion-ghost-town-netflix-filming-mole-forest-city-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719888051000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6683687c1aace5b3ada36b5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%