20on%20Fox%20Nation%2C%20the%20conservative%20broadcaster's%20online%20platform%20owned%20by%20the%20family%20of%20media%20mogul%20Rupert%20Murdoch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20dramatized%20version%20of%20a%20criminal%20trial%2C%20the%20series%20contained%20a%20warning%20the%20proceedings%20were%20fiction%2C%20depicting%20the%20first%20son%20being%20prosecuted%20for%20graft%20--%20accusations%20that%20have%20been%20made%20for%20years%20by%20Donald%20Trump%20supporters%20who%20point%20to%20Hunter%20Biden's%20past%20business%20ties%20with%20Ukraine%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accusations%20have%20never%20led%20to%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20series%20integrates%20real%20images%20of%20Biden%2C%20%26quot%3Bdepicting%20him%20in%20the%20nude%2C%20depicting%20an%20unclothed%20or%20exposed%20intimate%20part%20of%20him%2C%20as%20well%20as%20engaged%20in%20sex%20acts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFox%20published%20and%20disseminated%20these%20intimate%20images%20to%20its%20vast%20audience%20of%20millions%20as%20part%20of%20an%20entertainment%20program%20in%20order%20to%20humiliate%2C%20harass%2C%20annoy%20and%20alarm%20Mr.%20Biden%20and%20to%20tarnish%20his%20reputation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20images%20originated%20from%20a%20laptop%20that%20Hunter%20Biden%20dropped%20off%20at%20a%20computer%20repair%20shop%2C%20but%20which%20he%20never%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20contents%20have%20been%20circulating%20ever%20since%2C%20and%20are%20the%20subject%20of%20widespread%20conspiracy%20theories%20as%20well%20as%20embarrassing%20fodder%20for%20the%20political%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20entirely%20politically%20motivated%20lawsuit%20is%20devoid%20of%20merit%2C%26quot%3B%20Fox%20News%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Biden%20did%20not%20complain%20about%20(it)%20until%20sending%20a%20letter%20in%20late%20April%202024.%20The%20program%20was%20removed%20within%20days%20of%20the%20letter%2C%20in%20an%20abundance%20of%20caution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsistent%20with%20the%20First%20Amendment%2C%20Fox%20News%20has%20accurately%20covered%20the%20newsworthy%20events%20of%20Mr.%20Biden's%20own%20making%2C%20and%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20vindicating%20our%20rights%20in%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHunter%20Biden%20was%20convicted%20by%20a%20jury%20in%20June%20of%20illegal%20possession%20of%20a%20firearm%20in%20a%20federal%20trial%20that%20again%20brought%20to%20light%20his%20years%20of%20addiction%20to%20alcohol%2C%20cocaine%20and%20crack%20cocaine%2C%20apparent%20in%20many%20of%20the%20images%20discovered%20on%20the%20laptop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%20he%20will%20face%20a%20separate%20tax%20fraud%20case%2C%20a%20trial%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20distract%20from%20his%20father's%20presidential%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719888000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fhdfbn7go_hunter-biden-_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-president-joe-bidens-son-hunter-sues-fox-news-for-airing-revenge-porn-6014457%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20son%20Hunter%20is%20suing%20right-wing%20Fox%20News%20for%20airing%20nude%20images%20of%20him%20in%20a%20miniseries%20that%20he%20claims%20amount%20to%20%26quot%3Brevenge%20porn%2C%26quot%3B%20court%20documents%20showed%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-president-joe-bidens-son-hunter-sues-fox-news-for-airing-revenge-porn-6014457%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-