2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20was%20clear%20this%20sandwich%20wasn't%20just%20thrown%20together.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22portillos%20sandwich%20with%20tape%20measure%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fc1590d3535b001991dc72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Portillo's%20sandwich%20was%20thick%20and%20delicious.%3Cp%3EAlexis%20Kishimoto%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flavors%20of%20the%20beef%20tasted%20like%20they%20were%20developed%20and%20created%20over%20time%20during%20a%20slow%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20bread%20that%20kept%20the%20beef%20in%20place%20was%20soft%20and%20fluffy%20but%20crusty%20on%20the%20outside%2C%20which%20allowed%20for%20the%20tender%20beef%20to%20nicely%20mingle%20with%20the%20pillowy%20inside.%20It%20smelled%20and%20tasted%20freshly%20baked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20like%20I%20could%20taste%20the%20time%2C%20effort%2C%20and%20care%20that%20was%20put%20into%20this%20sandwich%2C%20which%20was%20extra%20surprising%20considering%20how%20busy%20the%20chain%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20Portillo's%20beef%20was%20worth%20waiting%20for.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22portillos%20sandwich%20on%20paper%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fc15b6d3535b001991dc7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPortillo's%20sandwich%20was%20flavorful%20and%20juicy.%3Cp%3EAlexis%20Kishimoto%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeasured%20length%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%206%20inches%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeasured%20width%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202%201%2F2%20inches%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWait%20time%20to%20order%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20nine%20minutes%2C%2023%20seconds%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWait%20time%20for%20beef%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20three%20minutes%2C%2048%20secon