%20around%20me%20and%20what%20is%20my%20future%20going%20to%20look%20like%20were%20always%20on%20her%20mind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20every%20time%20doubt%20took%20centre%20stage%2C%20she%20toughened%20her%20resolve%20to%20overcome%20it%2C%20thinking%20to%20herself%20%E2%80%98I%20can%20do%20this%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20spark%20of%20hope%20kept%20her%20dreams%20alive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20the%20case%20of%20any%20race%2C%20cheerleaders%20are%20essential.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20I%20had%20invaluable%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sakshi%20referring%20to%20her%20mother%2C%20father%2C%20sister%20and%20grandparents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20ensured%20they%20were%20positive%20when%20around%20her%2C%20it%20was%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Sneha%20points%20out%2C%20watching%20one%E2%80%99s%20child%20in%20pain%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20difficult%20things%20to%20go%20through%20as%20a%20parent.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20day%20came%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354377%2Fkerala-r-vishwan-honey-farmer-abandoned-child-bee-rearing-beekeeping-training-profits-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20challenge%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20broke%20down%20many%20times%20seeing%20the%20pain%20she%20was%20in.%20It%20was%20heartbreaking%20to%20watch%20an%20all-rounder%20and%20multi-talented%20girl%20not%20even%20being%20able%20to%20sit%2C%20stand%20or%20hold%20anything.%20The%20initial%20days%20were%20so%20tough%20that%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20think%20or%20comprehend%20anything.%20I%20would%20simply%20follow%20the%20instructions%20given%20to%20me.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1719488477.jpg%5C%22%20width%3