of%20land%20planted%20with%20bitter%20gourd%20will%20give%20a%20farmer%20roughly%20the%20same%20income%20as%20one%20hectare%20planted%20for%20rice.%20Vegetables%20can%20be%20harvested%20quickly%20(45-55%20days)%2C%20and%203-4%20crops%20can%20be%20cultivated%20throughout%20the%20year%20to%20meet%20the%20increased%20demand%20for%20vegetables%20and%20changes%20in%20food%20consumption.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFarming%20is%20a%20viable%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20Smarika%20has%20been%20cultivating%20a%20variety%20of%20vegetables%20on%20her%20land.%20She%20now%20plans%20to%20add%2015%20acres%20more%20this%20year%20to%20her%20existing%2020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smarika%20plans%20to%20expand%20the%20area%20under%20vegetable%20cultivation.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354729%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESmarika%20plans%20to%20expand%20the%20area%20under%20vegetable%20cultivation.