ops%20for%20private%20and%20government%20schools%2C%20business%20organisations%2C%20neighbourhood%20groups%20and%20for%20under-resourced%20communities%20as%20well%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20experience%20has%20shown%20that%20the%20questions%2C%20beliefs%2C%20challenges%2C%20and%20desires%20of%20parents%20are%20remarkably%20universal%3A%20every%20parent%20wants%20the%20best%20for%20their%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FFi-1719405849.gif%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Balancing%20the%20financial%20and%20emotional%20support%20aspects%20of%20parenting.%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354442%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20which%20are%20the%20lessons%20that%20have%20impacted%20parents%20the%20most%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20the%20top%20ten%20concepts%20that%20have%20transformed%20their%20lives%20and%20relationships%20with%20their%20children%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EParents%20are%20brain%20architects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%93%20Many%20parents%20are%20astonished%20to%20learn%20that%20their%20actions%20significantly%20influence%20their%20child%E2%80%99s%20brain%20development.%20This%20realisation%20often%20sparks%20a%20deep%20interest%20in%20understanding%20how%20to%20nurture%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20brains%20effectively.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20have%20seen%20how%20brain%20science%2C%20irrespective%20of%20a%20parent%E2%80%99s%20educational%20background%2C%20becomes%20an%20empowering%20tool%20that%20propels%20them%20to%20try%20and%20provide%20a%20safe%20and%20nurturing%20environment%20for%20their%20child%E2%80%99s%20cognitive%20and%20emotional%20growth.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPause%20and%20take%20some%20deep%20breaths%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%93%20It%20may%20sound%20clich%C3%A9d%2C%20but%20parents%20who%20practise%20this%20see%20a%20transformation%20in%20how%20they%20react%20to%20their%20children.%20Learning%20to%20regulate%20anger%20has%20been%20life%20altering%20to%20many.%20Parents%20come%20back%20to%20share%20how%20that%20%E2%80%98pause%E2%80%99%2C%20along%20with%20the%20other%20tools%20that%20they%20learned%2C%20helped%20them%20calm%20down%20and%20deal%20with%20a%20tough%20situation%20(even%20with%20their%20spouses!).%20This%20tool%20breaks%20the%20cycle%20of%20violence%20against%20children.%20Violence%20in%20both%20words%20and%20deeds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPunishment%20and%20threats%20simply%20don%E2%80%99t%20work.%20There%20is%20another%20way%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMany%20parents%20regret%20yelling%20at%20or%20hitting%20their%20kids%3B%20it%20makes%20them%20feel%20terrible.%20However%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20conditioned%20to%20believe%20that%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20a%20good%20parent%20is%20required%20to%20do.%20If%20you%20are%20soft%2C%20your%20children%20are%20going%20to%20%E2%80%9Csit%20on%20your%20head%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EParents%20feel%20liberated%20when%20they%20discover%20that%20there%20are%20positive%20ways%20to%20discipline%20their%20children%20as%20well.%20Changing%20and%20breaking%20established%20patterns%20is%20not%20easy.%20It%20takes%20hard%20work%20but%20once%20they%20make%20the%20change%2C%20they%20share%20with%20delight%20how%20connection%20and%20collaboration%20with%20the%20child%20works%20much%20better%20than%20force.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmpathy%20is%20key%20to%20building%20trust%20and%20connection%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20does%20my%20child%20lie%20to%20me%20and%20hide%20things%20from%20me%E2%80%9D