0child%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECorporate%20entities%20also%20recognise%20the%20value%20of%20parenting%20workshops%20in%20promoting%20work-life%20balance%20and%20stress%20reduction%20among%20employees.%20Schools%20similarly%20offer%20these%20workshops%20to%20empower%20parents%20in%20creating%20supportive%20home%20environments%2C%20positively%20influencing%20academic%2C%20social%2C%20and%20behavioural%20aspects%20of%20child%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20movement%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332417%2Fhow-to-fight-for-children-rights-lgbtqia-community-stories-of-acceptance-support-of-parents%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparent%20education%20is%20pivotal%20for%20a%20family%E2%80%99s%20well-being%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20mental%20health%2C%20and%20the%20future%20of%20society.%20Advocating%20for%20parent%20education%20as%20an%20accessible%20fundamental%20right%20across%20all%20socio-economic%20groups%20is%20crucial.%20By%20supporting%20parents%20in%20raising%20their%20children%2C%20we%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20a%20better%20world%20and%20a%20better%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(This%20article%20is%20written%20by%20Kesang%20Menezes%20of%20Parenting%20Matters%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%3Cem%3E%20Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EParenting%20Matters%20is%20deeply%20committed%20to%20building%20a%20world%20where%20children%20can%20thrive%20to%20their%20fullest%20potential.%20They%20believe%20that%20informed%20and%20connected%20parenting%20is%20crucial%20for%20individual%20growth%2C%20community%20well-being%2C%20and%20societal%20progress.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETheir%20core%20mission%20is%20to%20empower%20parents%20to%20create%20nurturing%20families.%20With%20a%20team%20of%2012%20certified%20parent%20educators%20having%20two%20decades%20of%20experience%2C%20they%20have%20transformed%20the%20lives%20of%20over%201%20lakh%20famil