village%20across%20the%20district%20organising%20health%20camps.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiturekha%20says%20that%20with%20solar%20energy%2C%20the%20crew%20has%20an%20uninterrupted%20power%20supply%20for%20a%20long%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Saddam%2C%20who%20remains%20in%20the%20boat%20for%20at%20least%20nine%20days%20on%20a%20stretch%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20solar-powered%20chilling%20units%20are%20very%20beneficial%20as%20without%20them%2C%20we%20could%20not%20keep%20the%20vaccines%20for%20more%20than%20three%20days.%20Besides%2C%20it%20is%20really%20helpful%20in%20running%20fans%20all%20day%20as%20it%20is%20extremely%20hot%20and%20humid%20in%20the%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20feel%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20solar%20panels%20should%20be%20increased%20for%20better%20results.%20Last%20night%2C%20the%20solar-powered%20fans%20could%20only%20last%20till%209%3A30.%20We%20had%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20generator%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20night.%20If%20the%20capacity%20is%20increased%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20retire%20to%20bed%20and%20sleep%20peacefully%20after%20a%20hectic%20day%20providing%20quality%20service%20to%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20healthcare%20provider%20believes%20the%20capacity%20must%20be%20increased%2C%20Riturekha%20says%20that%20with%20the%20additional%20support%20of%20solar%20energy%2C%20the%20floating%20health%20clinic%20is%20successfully%20catering%20to%20about%2010%2C000%20patients%20in%20the%20district%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20soil%20erosion%20and%20regular%20flooding%20in%20the%20region%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20challenge%20to%20build%20a%20permanent%20structure%20in%20these%20places%20which%20leads%20to%20medical%20apathy%20for%20the%20residents.%20But%20with%20these%20boat%20clinics%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20bridge%20the%20healthcare%20divide%20in%20remote%20areas%20of%20the%20islands%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Riturekha%20Barua%20and%20Dr%20Saddam%20Hussain.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719404622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-2-1719399558.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354362%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20reporting%20from%20rural%20parts%20of%20Assam%2C%20Sanjoy%20Hazarika%20noticed%20the%20intense%20need%20for%20a%20sustained%20healthcare%20system%20in%20the%20region.%20In%20collaboration%20with%20the%20National%20Rural%20Health%20Mission%2C%20his%20non-profit%2C%20C-NES%2C%20launched%20boat%20clinics%20in%202005%20to%20bridge%20the%20healthcare%20divide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354362%2Fboat-health-clinics-solar-energy-on-brahmaputra-river-assam-sanjoy-hazarika%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20To%20Make%20a%20UPSC%20CSE%20Prep%20Timetable%20That%20Works%3F%20IAS%20Officer%20Shares%20Her%20Secret%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E7%3A10%20pm%3Cbr%3E10%20October%2C%202022%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20Civil%20Service%20Exam%20(CSE)%202021%20were%20announced%2C%20bringing%20squeals%20of%20happiness%2C%20tears%2C%20and%20bear%20hugs%20to%20the%20Pandey%20household%20in%20Jamtara%2C%20Jharkhand.%20Taruni%20had%20cleared%20the%20exam%20and%20was%20on%20her%20way%20to%20becoming%20a%20civil%20servant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20celebration%20was%20even%20more%20remarkable%20because%20this%20was%20her%20first%20and%20last%20attempt%3B%20at%2032%2C%20she%20prepared%20for%20the%20exam%20in%20just%20six%20months%20without%20any%20coaching!%20She%20accomplished%20this%20feat%20through%20a%20self-devised%20strategy%20th