%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347611%2Fupsc-cse-2023-final-list-toppers-ias-officer-jitin-yadav-viral-tweet-on-failure-aspirants-inspiration%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprepare%20a%20timetable%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20the%20number%20of%20hours%20of%20study%2C%20Taruni%E2%80%99s%20plan%20focussed%20on%20the%20portion%20to%20complete%20each%20day.%20Some%20days%2C%20it%20took%20less%20time%2C%20while%20other%20days%2C%20it%20took%20more.%20Even%20while%20sharing%20her%20strategy%2C%20she%20emphasises%20that%20everyone%20is%20different%20and%20must%20plan%20accordingly.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20copy%20anyone.%20Play%20on%20your%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20a%20few%20tips%20to%20keep%20your%20mind%20calm%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStudy%20smarter%20and%20study%20harder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolve%20previous%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20(PYQ)%20papers%20and%20understand%20the%20topics%20UPSC%20has%20loved%20all%20these%20years.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20PYQs%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20mean%20just%20the%20questions%20but%20also%20the%20options.%20Observe%20why%20a%20question%20has%20been%20asked%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20seeing%20what%20has%20been%20asked%2C%20to%20understand%20the%20psyche%20of%20the%20question%20paper%20setter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20stop%2C%20but%20learn%20when%20to%20let%20go%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaruni%20quit%20her%20MBBS%20after%20two%20years%20due%20to%20a%20health%20problem.%20%E2%80%9CNever%20giving%20up%20is%20a%20good%20attitude%20that%20we%20all%20have%20been%20taught%20since%20we%20were%20kids.%20I%20made%20a%20similar%20mistake%20by%20not%20leaving%20my%20MBBS%20course%20early%20because%20I%20always%20felt%20that%20if%20I%20quit%2C%20it%20would%20be%20my%20failure.%20I%20realised